Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.54,0:01:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.11,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#26         稔、柚姬         談論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.32,0:01:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常像ちぃ的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.98,0:01:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.92,0:02:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太像是惡作劇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.56,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後還有其他\N與寄圖者有關的線索嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，暫時還沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬妳不需要道歉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.84,0:02:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再確認一次看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能調出收到這張圖當天的資料嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.05,0:02:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會發現些什麼也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.16,0:02:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片怎麼看都像是ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.24,0:02:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看起來很像ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這堆亂七八糟的是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.38,0:02:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒看過這種接頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.55,0:02:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是惡作劇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某處看過ちぃ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先拍下她的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.15,0:03:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後合成出這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過總覺得其中並不單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.06,0:03:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被手郲住的這個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.80,0:03:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是“C”的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.87,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C、H、O、B、         I、T…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我之前應該跟你說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.08,0:03:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以“Chobits”為代號的\N那台傳說中的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠自己思考行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.72,0:03:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有人的外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻又不是人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.89,0:03:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.81,0:04:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.91,0:04:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是惡作劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒必要操這個心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.54,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ自己也不記得這張圖片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實根本談不上什麼記憶\N因為資料跟OS都不存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能否讓我插句話呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.46,0:04:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新查詢看看\Nちぃ至今做過的事如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.76,0:04:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許會發現\Nちぃ與圖片的關連性也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.61,0:05:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和，你問她一下電話號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先別管那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳知道我的電話號碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.02,0:05:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,03-68828-52DF3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.82,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說話了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次講出“ちぃ”以外的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.89,0:05:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她有安裝學習軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.00,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是被丟在垃圾堆裡，對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是在被丟掉前初始化了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣\N但學習機能卻還留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果好好教她\N我想她不但能夠說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.51,0:05:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能夠做其他事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你好好教她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她現在的主人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會按 照你教她的方式行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.86,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽會時的暗號遭到利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘遭妻子殺害的女人怨念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.02,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今仍徘徊在那間公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.99,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跟她遇害當天\N同樣的悶熱陰天裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就會發出那個暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人以前所用的幽會暗號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將房間的電燈關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關了又開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在那裡等待著新的犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.15,0:06:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在G公寓的104號房裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那間不應該有的104號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.83,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.06,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬼故事\N說的果然就是GAB城崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去GAB城崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去上面看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.51,0:07:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.68,0:07:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.92,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體動不了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快動，快動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.85,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倉庫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為最近東西容易發霉潮濕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想來個大掃除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是電燈泡快要壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒辦法打掃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了換燈泡\N我找來了各種東西墊腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還是碰不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.01,0:08:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會叫我來幫忙換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.18,0:08:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.48,0:08:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是從門下面\N流出的黑色液體…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我搬桌子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.29,0:08:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我有上去找本須和幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來好像很忙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電燈泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會有104號房？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.47,0:08:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來一樓本來有四間房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁是103號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我搬來時做了一點改裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.18,0:09:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺的是102號房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然被搞得團團轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.79,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不害怕了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.66,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.95,0:09:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.02,0:09:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大魔王終於登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.49,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼強嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看雜誌和網路上的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒看過有人打倒過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警告，警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過這裡就可以到下個城鎮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別想不開了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打不贏那傢伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.52,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.26,0:10:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,carbonara
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chorizo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.82,0:10:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.17,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.50,0:11:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時ちぃ明明沒有經驗值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻打倒了遊戲裡的大魔王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和也不可能會寫這種程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.58,0:11:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道她真的不是普通的電腦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那個妳有看到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.25,0:12:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹看到海豚的“嘩啦”\N會很高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.22,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.93,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.69,0:13:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.85,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.77,0:13:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從表面看來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像也沒進水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會生氣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真是台不可思議的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般如果掉到海裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會進水，然後會很難修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ的相關記憶資料到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.99,0:14:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們果然還是\N有點資料不足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.79,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找新保幫忙看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過新保少爺他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保，新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天先出門了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也很睏的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清…清水老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我住一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫那麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.59,0:15:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.39,0:16:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.36,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有時會早到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她從來沒遲到過的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.97,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我接通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個聲音，你是新保對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在搞什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟老師私奔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵架啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很久沒有吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者應該說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連話都說不上兩句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上了門鍊就表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.66,0:17:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老公忘了我會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不在家都沒影響了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.65,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得怎樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得怎樣都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明在說這麼傷心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她卻沒有哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她其實很想哭出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是拼命在忍耐罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.39,0:18:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.42,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想至少讓她在遇到\N不愉快或傷心的事時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠哭個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此，為什麼要私奔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道只剩這個方法了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們這個年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.84,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許就如同你所說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是我的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得不相信男人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她認為就算一開始說喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦出現像電腦那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會完全改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像從沒喜歡過一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.37,0:19:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓她跑掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.01,0:19:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定私奔到深山的溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好地方喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣濕答答的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩愛愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說，這算是私奔啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多香子點頭之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點頭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.52,0:19:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.86,0:19:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再婚是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.93,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉再幫我保管一段時間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫你保管當然沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜囉，本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再跟你聯絡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再有什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.75,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種重考生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過或許我可以幫上什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.92,0:20:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.95,0:20:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.13,0:20:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像電腦那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以迎合自己的對象啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.75,0:20:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，讓我幫您泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.35,0:20:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是休息一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我這並不是累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.17,0:21:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我當時分析ちぃ沒失敗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.98,0:21:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經做得很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.49,0:21:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假使這孩子學會了說話\N學會了做各種不同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.26,0:21:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縱使她再怎麼乖巧\N再怎麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.47,0:21:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勸你還是別喜歡上她比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.97,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想在日後\N傷心流淚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.91,0:21:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口味…不對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.38,0:21:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是用跟姊姊同樣的方法泡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.06,0:22:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.97,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.74,0:22:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.06,0:23:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.82,0:23:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.19,0:23:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.26,0:23:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.01,0:23:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
